Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.77,Guard,,0,0,0,,It's Princess Luna and Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:10.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Everfree Forest is… invading?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:15.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting to get a pretty good idea of who we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:17.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm reformed, don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:20.41,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask your zebra friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.28,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You can turn the potion from purple to white.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:27.32,Zecora,,0,0,0,,You may see why the sky is day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:28.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:31.82,Luna,,0,0,0,,There can only be one princess in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.64,Luna,,0,0,0,,And that princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,WILL BE ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luna! Think of how long you were banished to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:49.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You give us no choice but to send you back there if you don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:51.59,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Luna! I will not fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.08,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You must lower the moon! It is your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.76,Luna,,0,0,0,,Luna…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:00.75,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.33,Luna,,0,0,0,,I have but one royal duty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.63,Luna,,0,0,0,,TO DESTROY YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.28,Luna,,0,0,0,,And where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Celestia!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why would Luna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Oh dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,, I'm sorry, but you have given me no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.58,Celestia,,0,0,0,, but to use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are those…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the Elements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But that's how they looked in…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the past…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the night you banished her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:12.05,Luna,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why are you all looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,you were mumbling to yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.52,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, and don't forget the uncontrollable sobbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.62,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We were really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,I for one found it delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,Sort of a one-pony theatre piece, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:46.13,Discord,,0,0,0,,You should really consider taking it on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Did you find out whose rump we need to kick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and where we can find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I saw something from a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but it didn't explain what's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.19,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Perhaps further back still \N are the answers you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.82,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Another sip of the potion \N will give you a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:05.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I do hope she breaks into a song this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:30.99,Discord,,0,0,0,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,How about a game of "Pin-a-tail-on-the-pony"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.72,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Playtime is over for you, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:41.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.93,Discord,,0,0,0,,Suit yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:05:58.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,What have you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.22,Luna,,0,0,0,,With them we shall defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:06.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This must be when they turned Discord into stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,You should see yourselves right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.84,Discord,,0,0,0,,Expressions on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:16.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,So intense, so sure of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,Hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.88,Luna,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My cutiemark!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.23,Luna,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:59.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We have managed to discover the only means by which we can defeat Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.39,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and free the citizens of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.81,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Even without these elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:07.22,Celestia,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Harmony will possess a powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.60,Celestia,,0,0,0,,As long as that magic remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:18.20,Celestia,,0,0,0,,it will continue to control and contain all that grows here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, what'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what happened to Princess Luna and Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I think I know why the Everfree Forest is acting this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:36.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something's happened to the Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The Tree of what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's where Princess Luna and Princess Celestia found the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I think it's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's go save a…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where is it exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I think it's in…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.57,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need more popcorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Seems like only yesterday we were heading
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,into these woods to find the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seems like only yesterday I was foolish enough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to think I should go after them on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we are going to face in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but whatever it is - I know we need to face it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We can use those to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,A crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,A little too close, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You sure you're alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just can't seem to get these new wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to do what I want them to do when I want it them to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You'll figure it out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:23.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Eventuall isn't soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You had been having an awful lot of trouble with those things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and, well, who knows what else is gonna come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:34.53,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You know, maybe it wouldn't be such a bad idea for Twilight to come back to Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and let us look for the Tree of Harmony without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,For starters, you just about got eaten by a crocodilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We all did. He wasn't after just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Sure but, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,the rest of us aren't princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia and Princess Luna are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,If something happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:58.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I just don't think Equestria can risk losing another princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:01.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Applejack does make a valid point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Even if we manage to save the Tree of Harmony,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't necesserily mean Princess Celestia and Princess Luna will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Equestria will need somepony to lead in their absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:14.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But the Tree of Harmony! I'm the only one who has seen it and knows what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Huge tree? Cutiemarks on the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Probably being attacked by something hideously awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah? I'm pretty sure we'll know it when we see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All of you feel this way? Feel like I shouldn't be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It is probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,HEEELP! HEEELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:56.11,Discord,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!\NNo luck finding your tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We ran into some trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:02.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and my friends decided it would be best if I return to Ponyville while they continue the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:07.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Equestria will need me if Princess Celestia and Princess Luna don't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm just surprised that you agreed to their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:15.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd be the kind of pony who would think she was better than everypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm better than anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, how silly of me to assume that you'd think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:25.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,All you did was: chose to keep your precious princess self
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:29.66,Discord,,0,0,0,,out of harm's way while your friends thrust themselves wide into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:35.40,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll all be the best of pals again when they return from their terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:39.98,Discord,,0,0,0,,yet deeply bonding experience that they're having without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I never should've agreed to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:51.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,C'mon Twilight, Discord may be reformed but he's not that reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,He's just trying to get under your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, it's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Anypony else starting to think this is a lost cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're almost at Celestia and Luna's old castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:14.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe whatever Twilight saw when she took that crazy potion wasn't real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's no tree of harmony? Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's right down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to get to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Take the stairs, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:42.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know where we are. We're lost! I never should've left my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,We can't just give up. Maybe if I get up there I'l be able to spot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,, I think it's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So let's save it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:20.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Valiant efforts on both your parts, but the tree remains in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I suppose you got a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know who would know what to do! But we sent her home…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It was your idea, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:45.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We all agreed it was the best thing, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We were trying to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Trouble! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.86,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Listen here, you rabid rhododendrons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:16.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You mess with one of us — you mess with all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I sure am glad you came looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not as glad as I am that you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:52.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The truth of it is, Twilight, we're simply lost without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:55.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Equestria may need its princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But we need our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Even without these elements, the Tree of Harmony will possess a powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:29.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,As long as that magic remains, it will continue to control and contain all that grows here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:37.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,, I know how we can save the tree. We have to give it the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to protect Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:47.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How are we meant to rein Discord in if we can't use the Elements to turn him back to stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:52.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight. The Elements of Harmony, they would keep us connected no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right about one thing, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:58.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony did bring us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it isn't the elements that will keep us connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:05.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's our friendship. And it's more important and more powerful than any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:09.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My new role in Equestria may mean I have to take on new responsibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:14.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and our friendships may be tested, but it will never ever be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose. Everypony ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:45.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Aw, phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,We know how difficult it must've been for you to give up the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It took great courage to relinquish them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:19.35,Luna,,0,0,0,,What's inside it? How am I supposed to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Six locks, six keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:28.70,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I do not know where they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,but I do know that it is a mystery you will not be solving alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.01,Discord,,0,0,0,,Bravo, ladies, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:45.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,How ever did you save the day this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,Brfash the beastie with your magic necklaces, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,Where are those little trinkets of yours? You know, the ones you used to send me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,back to my extremely uncomfortable stone prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,Gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:19:00.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But our friendship remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.01,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And if you wanna remain friends you'll
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:06.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,stop thinking whatever it is you thinking and help us clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:09.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fine. But I don't do windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:14.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,One thing I don't get, why did all this happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.97,Discord,,0,0,0,,Those seeds I planted should've spurted up ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:26.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why should I try to explain when you can see for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Playtime is over for you, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:41.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, I doubt that. Hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously things didn't go according to my original plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.76,Discord,,0,0,0,,My plunder seeds should've stolen the magic from the Tree of Harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:54.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,and captured Princess Celestia and Princess Luna thousands of moons ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:58.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,Alas, it seems, the tree have enough magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.27,Discord,,0,0,0,,to keep the seeds from growing up big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.13,Discord,,0,0,0,,Until now, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:09.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You realize this is information we could've used hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:13.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,And rob you of a valuable lesson about being princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,What kind of a friend do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:39.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Citizens of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.44,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It is no longer with a heavy heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:45.41,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but with great joy that I raise the summer sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:50.29,Celestia,,0,0,0,,For this celebration now represents not the defeat of Nightmare Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:54.53,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but the return of my sister, Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.95,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVYI` PONETC
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:37.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon 2 anon \Nsunnysubs.com
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That time will come one day\NYou'll see when we can all be friends
